=== 國際米蘭 ===

2021年5月，艾歷臣跟隨國際米蘭以11分的差距力壓群雄，奪下睽違11年的義甲冠軍，而他終於獲得人生首個頂級聯賽冠軍。登頂後數日，[[国际米兰足球俱乐部|国际米兰]]班主[[張康陽|張康陽]]卻要求主帥與球員們減薪，孔蒂不願配合憤而辭職，不少奪冠功臣亦據傳下賽季將離隊。<ref name="冠軍">{{cite news|url=https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E9%AB%94%E8%82%B2/article/20210510/s00015/1620584211941/%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%B1%B3%E8%98%AD%E5%B0%87%E5%B8%A5%E5%82%B3%E6%8B%92%E6%B8%9B%E8%96%AA%E6%81%90%E6%98%9F%E6%95%A3|title=國際米蘭將帥傳拒減薪恐星散|date=2021-05-10|accessdate=2021-05-12|work=明報|language=zh-hk|archive-date=2021-07-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210722035715/https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E9%AB%94%E8%82%B2/article/20210510/s00015/1620584211941/%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%B1%B3%E8%98%AD%E5%B0%87%E5%B8%A5%E5%82%B3%E6%8B%92%E6%B8%9B%E8%96%AA%E6%81%90%E6%98%9F%E6%95%A3}}</ref>

在埃里克森尚未做出決定之前，他隨同丹麥國家隊的隊友先參加了延期一年舉行的歐洲盃，然而他在歐洲盃小組賽第一場比賽便因心臟問題倒下送醫。雖然手術後狀況良好，然而根據義甲的球員健康規定，必須依靠心臟去顫器的球員將無法在義大利出賽。於是2021年12月，仍打算繼續球員生涯的埃里克森不得不和國際米蘭解約，以尋找允許他上場的聯賽。<ref>{{Cite news|title=Inter Milan terminate Eriksen contract|language=en-GB|work=BBC Sport|url=https://www.bbc.com/sport/football/59699440|date=2021-12-17|accessdate=2021-12-18|archive-date=2022-04-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220414185519/https://www.bbc.com/sport/football/59699440}}</ref>

===布伦特福德===
2022年1月31日，英超球队[[布伦特福德足球俱乐部|布伦特福德]]宣布签下埃里克森，合同期6个月，合约期满后可选择延长至2023年6月。埃里克森得以重返英超并延续自己的职业生涯。<ref>{{Cite news|last=Amako|first=Uche|date=2022-01-31|title=Transfer Deadline Day 2022 live: Brentford sign Christian Eriksen - latest updates|language=en-GB|work=The Telegraph|url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/football/2022/01/31/transfer-news-deadline-day-2022-live-latest-premier-league/|access-date=2022-01-31|issn=0307-1235|archive-date=2022-06-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220602081151/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/football/2022/01/31/transfer-news-deadline-day-2022-live-latest-premier-league/}}</ref>4月2日，埃里克森在客場4-1戰勝同城死敵[[切尔西足球俱乐部|切爾西]]的比賽中打進了他重返英超聯賽的首個進球。<ref>{{Cite web |title=Chelsea 1-4 Brentford: Christian Eriksen scores as Bees seal incredible derby win at Stamford Bridge |url=https://www.skysports.com/football/chelsea-vs-brentford/report/446590 |date=2022-04-02 |website=Sky Sports |language=en |access-date=2022-04-02 |archive-date=2022-04-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220404134955/https://www.skysports.com/football/chelsea-vs-brentford/report/446590 }}</ref>

==國際賽==
[[File:Eriksen_Euro_2012.jpg|thumb]]為[[丹麥國家足球隊|丹麥]]上陣的艾歷臣]]
2007年7月，艾歷臣獲{{Link-en|丹麥17歲以下國家足球隊|Denmark national under-17 football team|丹麥U17}}徵召<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.dbu.dk/news/newsShow.aspx?id=239942 |title=U/17-landsholdet til Internordisk Cup |publisher=DBU.dk |date=2007-07-09 |accessdate=2010-06-06 |language=da |archive-date=2015-04-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150428115856/http://www.dbu.dk/news/newsShow.aspx?id=239942 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，他在7月31日的處子戰的表現亦使人印象深刻<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.dbu.dk/news/newsShow.aspx?id=240235 |title=Tre point mod Færøerne |publisher=DBU.dk |date=2007-07-31 |accessdate=2010-06-06 |language=da |archive-date=2015-04-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150428115259/http://www.dbu.dk/news/newsShow.aspx?id=240235 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2008年，他在U17組別賽事上陣16次取得9個入球，獲選為[[丹麥足球協會|丹麥年度U17天才球員]]<ref name="dbu">{{cite web |url=http://www.dbu.dk/news/newsShow.aspx?id=250290 |title=Lumb og Eriksen nyeste Arla Landsholdstalenter |publisher=DBU.dk |date=2008-12-05 |accessdate=2010-06-06 |language=da |archive-date=2015-04-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150428122205/http://www.dbu.dk/news/newsShow.aspx?id=250290 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他亦是四位丹麥2008年天才球員的候選人之一<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.dbu.dk/news/newsShow.aspx?id=249275 |title=Danmarks fire største talenter |publisher=DBU.dk |date=2008-10-24 |accessdate=2010-06-06 |language=da |archive-date=2014-11-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141107135944/http://www.dbu.dk/news/newsShow.aspx?id=249275 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，最終由[[馬迪亞斯·佐真遜|-{zh-hans:馬迪亞斯·佐真遜; zh-hk:馬迪亞斯·佐真遜;}-]]當選<ref name="dbu"/>。直至2009年2月，他代表丹麥U17上陣27次。在2009年，他總共代表[[丹麥國家足球隊|丹麥U18]]和[[丹麥國家足球隊|丹麥U19]]上陣8次。2011年，艾歷臣亦獲[[丹麥21歲以下國家足球隊|丹麥U21]]徵召參加在丹麥舉行的[[歐洲U-21足球錦標賽|歐洲U-21足球錦標賽]]，丹麥在分組賽止步，而艾歷臣則在對白俄羅斯一仗攻入一球。

2010年2月，艾歷臣首次獲[[丹麥國家足球隊|丹麥]]徵召<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bold.dk/nyt/Christian-Eriksen-Det-er-helt-vildt |title=Christian Eriksen: Det er helt vildt |publisher=Bold.dk |date=2010-02-26 |accessdate=2010-04-13 |language=da |archive-date=2014-11-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141107132636/http://www.bold.dk/nyt/Christian-Eriksen-Det-er-helt-vildt |dead-url=no }}</ref>，他在3月對[[澳洲國家足球隊|澳洲]]的友賽中處子上陣<ref name="debut">{{cite web |url=http://sporten-dyn.tv2.dk/article.php/id-29005205.html?rss |title=Eriksen: Helt specielt med debut – TV 2 Sporten |publisher=Sporten-dyn.tv2.dk |date= |accessdate=2010-04-13 |language=da |archive-date=2020-08-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200825174710/https://sport.tv2.dk/fodbold/article.php/id-29005205.html?rss= |dead-url=no }}</ref>，成為丹麥隊歷年來第四年輕的國腳<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.haslund.info/danmark/aovs/ydeb.asp |title=A-landsholdspillere - Yngste debutant |publisher=www.haslund.info |date= |accessdate=2010-05-18 |language=da |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110721203507/http://www.haslund.info/danmark/aovs/ydeb.asp |archivedate=2011-07-21 }}</ref>。5月28日，丹麥領隊[[摩頓·奧臣|摩頓·奧臣]]宣佈他入選[[2010年世界盃|2010年世界盃]]丹麥隊最後的23人名單<ref>{{en}}{{cite web |url=http://www.uefa.com/worldcup/news/newsid=1493391.html |title=Olsen names final Denmark squad |publisher=UEFA.com |date=2010-05-28 |accessdate=2010-06-02 |archive-date=2014-12-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141221113724/http://www.uefa.com/worldcup/news/newsid=1493391.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他因而成為最年輕的參賽球員<ref name="youngest"/><ref name="youngest2"/>在世界盃，艾歷臣在分別對[[荷蘭國家足球隊|荷蘭]]及[[日本國家足球隊|日本]]時上陣，但丹麥最終未能突破分組賽階段。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.soccerway.com/matches/2010/06/14/world/world-cup/netherlands/denmark/878795/ |title=Netherlands vs. Denmark |publisher=Soccerway |date=2010-11-17 |accessdate=2011-02-11 |archive-date=2014-11-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141107163159/http://www.soccerway.com/matches/2010/06/14/world/world-cup/netherlands/denmark/878795/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.soccerway.com/matches/2010/06/24/world/world-cup/denmark/japan/878799/ |title=Denmark vs. Japan |publisher=Soccerway |date=2010-06-24 |accessdate=2011-02-11 |archive-date=2014-11-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141107165017/http://www.soccerway.com/matches/2010/06/24/world/world-cup/denmark/japan/878799/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2011年2月9日，丹麥主場負於英格蘭的比賽中，艾歷臣被評為全場最佳球員。賽後不少知名球壇人士皆稱讚他的表現，包括[[切尔西足球俱乐部|車路士]]球星[[法蘭·林柏特|-{zh-hans:弗兰克·兰帕德;zh-hk:法蘭克·林柏特;zh-tw:法蘭克·蘭帕德;}-]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://spn.dk/fodbold/landshold/article2335072.ece |title=Stjerne: Eriksen kan blive topspiller |publisher=spn.dk |date=2011-02-09 |accessdate=2011-02-10 |language=da |archive-date=2012-05-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120531014316/http://spn.dk/fodbold/landshold/article2335072.ece |dead-url=yes }}</ref>、曼聯球星[[里奧·費迪南|-{zh-hans:里奥·费迪南德;zh-hk:里奧·費迪南;zh-tw:里奧·費迪南德;}-]]（在Twitter）<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.sporten.dk/fodbold/ferdinand-skamroser-eriksen-paa-twitter |title=Ferdinand skamroser Eriksen på Twitter |publisher=Sporten.dk |date=2011-02-09 |accessdate=2011-02-10 |language=da |archive-date=2012-08-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120815172856/http://www.sporten.dk/fodbold/ferdinand-skamroser-eriksen-paa-twitter |dead-url=no }}</ref>、領隊[[摩頓·奧臣|摩頓·奧臣]]和數個英格蘭及丹麥的專業媒體。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://spn.dk/fodbold/landshold/article2335260.ece |title=Engelske medier jubler over Eriksen |publisher=spn.dk |date=2011-02-09 |accessdate=2011-02-10 |language=da |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110211205058/http://spn.dk/fodbold/landshold/article2335260.ece |archivedate=2011-02-11 }}</ref>2011年6月4日，艾歷臣攻入他第一個國家隊入球，協助丹麥在[[2012年歐洲國家盃外圍賽H組|歐洲國家盃外圍賽]]以2－0擊敗[[冰島國家足球隊|冰島]]。這個入球亦打破了丹麥球員在歐洲國家盃外圍賽的最年輕入球紀錄，比米高·勞特立在1983年所創的紀錄年輕9天。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ad.nl/ad/nl/1441/Ajax/article/detail/2441812/2011/06/06/Ajacied-Eriksen-speelt-Laudrup-uit-de-boeken.dhtml |title=Ajacied Eriksen speelt Laudrup uit de boeken |publisher=Ad.nl |date=2011-05-16 |accessdate=2011-06-06 |language=nl |archive-date=2015-05-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150501110904/http://www.ad.nl/ad/nl/1441/Ajax/article/detail/2441812/2011/06/06/Ajacied-Eriksen-speelt-Laudrup-uit-de-boeken.dhtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2020年10月14日，埃里克森在[[2020–21年歐洲國家聯賽A|歐洲國家聯賽]]對陣[[英格蘭足球代表隊|英格蘭]]的比賽達成第100次國家隊亮相。 
<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/football/2020/10/14/england-vs-denmark-uefa-nations-league-live-latest-updates/ |title=England vs Denmark, Uefa Nations League |accessdate=2020-10-14 |archive-date=2020-11-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201102113022/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/football/2020/10/14/england-vs-denmark-uefa-nations-league-live-latest-updates/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

埃里克森於2022年3月26日重返國家隊，在上半場以2-4負於[[荷蘭國家足球隊|荷蘭]]的比賽中上場，他在回歸後2分鐘打進一球。<ref>{{Cite news |title=Eriksen scores on Denmark return |language=en-GB |work=BBC Sport |url=https://www.bbc.com/sport/football/60889501 |date=2022-03-26 |accessdate=2022-04-02 |archive-date=2022-06-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220610170709/https://www.bbc.com/sport/football/60889501 }}</ref>

==意外==
[[哥本哈根|哥本哈根]]當地時間2021年6月12日傍晚，[[2020年歐洲足球錦標賽|2020年歐洲盃]][[2020年欧洲足球锦标赛B组#丹麦_vs_芬兰|B組丹麥對陣芬蘭的比賽]]第42分鐘，埃里克森在无身体对抗情况下倒地。队医赶来时有呼吸和脉搏，但随后[[心搏停止|心搏停止]]并需要[[心肺复苏|CPR]]急救，救护人员进行了一次[[去颤|去颤电击]]使其恢复心跳，<ref name="Guardian">{{Cite web |last=Christenson |first=Marcus |url=https://www.theguardian.com/football/2021/jun/13/he-was-gone-christian-eriksen-had-cardiac-arrest-denmark-doctor-says |title=‘He was gone’: Christian Eriksen had cardiac arrest, Denmark doctor says |date=2021-06-13 |access-date=2021-06-13 |work=The Guardian |archive-date=2021-06-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210627031804/https://www.theguardian.com/football/2021/jun/13/he-was-gone-christian-eriksen-had-cardiac-arrest-denmark-doctor-says }}</ref><ref name =Cardiac>{{Cite web|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/57458630|title=Eriksen suffered cardiac arrest - doctor|via=www.bbc.co.uk|access-date=2021-06-14|archive-date=2021-06-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210625153109/https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/57458630}}</ref>总共在球场上进行了近20分钟的急救使其恢复意识后送往医院，身体状况稳定。<ref>{{Cite news|last=Das|first=Andrew|date=2021-06-12|title=Denmark’s Christian Eriksen collapsed on the field against Finland.|language=en-US|work=The New York Times|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2021/06/12/sports/soccer/denmark-christian-eriksen-collapse.html|access-date=2021-06-12|issn=0362-4331|archive-date=2021-06-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210613024653/https://www.nytimes.com/2021/06/12/sports/soccer/denmark-christian-eriksen-collapse.html}}</ref><ref name="Sky News 12331132">{{cite news |title=Christian Eriksen: Denmark player 'awake and stabilised' in hospital after being given CPR following on-pitch collapse |url=https://news.sky.com/story/denmarks-christian-eriksen-given-cpr-after-collapsing-on-pitch-in-match-against-finland-12331132 |access-date=2021-06-12 |work=Sky News |date=2021-06-12 |archive-date=2021-06-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210622153838/https://news.sky.com/story/denmarks-christian-eriksen-given-cpr-after-collapsing-on-pitch-in-match-against-finland-12331132 }}</ref>经双方球员同意，比賽暂停一个半小时多后于当地时间20时30分继续进行。<ref>{{Cite web|title=The Latest: Belgium's Castagne to miss rest of Euro 2020|url=https://apnews.com/article/switzerland-europe-health-coronavirus-pandemic-international-soccer-91c0ba352d25986ac351ff285952b763|access-date=2021-06-13|date=2021-06-12|work=AP NEWS|publisher=[[美联社|美联社]]|language=en|archive-date=2021-07-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210706232356/https://apnews.com/article/switzerland-europe-health-coronavirus-pandemic-international-soccer-91c0ba352d25986ac351ff285952b763}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=B组-埃里克森遇惊魂|url=https://www.163.com/sports/article/GCBFJAMM00058781.html|access-date=2021-06-13|date=2021-06-13|last=|work=网易体育|language=zh|archive-date=2021-07-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210703002702/https://www.163.com/sports/article/GCBFJAMM00058781.html}}</ref>随后埃里克森接受了心脏除颤器植入手术，术后情况良好，并已出院，还亲自去看望了国家队队友<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://news.sky.com/story/christian-eriksen-visits-team-after-being-discharged-from-hospital-12336045 |title=Christian Eriksen visits teammates after discharge |date=2021-06-18 |access-date=2021-06-18 |work=Sky News |archive-date=2021-06-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210618211814/https://news.sky.com/story/christian-eriksen-visits-team-after-being-discharged-from-hospital-12336045 }}</ref>。

